d:
Hello, guys.

I just came here to introduce and post the first pages of my new series, Futa Breeders from Outer Space.

A quiet small town is suddenly receiving a visit from an enigmatic alien species. What are they really? What do they want? Whatever it is, it'll irreversibly change the lives of its inhabitants.

Since right now it does not have any smut scenes, I'll refrain from adding any tags; as the story progresses, I'll add them.

Right now, I plan to have it revolve around incest, futanari, dick growth, corruption, and gender bender. Of course, I can change this as the story goes on.

For those interested in the series, I publish pages for my patrons up to four weeks in advance, so there is almost a month of content already, as of this writing, May eleven, chapter 1 is about to end.
